                <text>A1, S1:  J. Mayo Williams, A. K. Salim, Green-Waldman, Herbie Mann, Van Heusen-Mercer, Oppenheim-McHugh-Fields&#13;
&#13;
A1, S2: Duke Ellington; John Coltrane; Dizzy Gillespie; Cole Porter; Shearing-Foster, Charlie Parker&#13;
&#13;
A2, S1:&#13;
G. &amp; I. Gershwin; Art Tatum (arranged); Dizzy Gillespie; Jose Ferrer; Thelonious Monk; Adriano Acea&#13;
&#13;
A2, S2: &#13;
William York; Green-Wolf; Lester Young, Basie-Rushing; Eckstine-Hines; Dietz-Schwartz</text>
